name: Animal Farm Dogs
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: Animal Farm Dogs (AFD) is a native farming token earned by staking in all non-native farms and pools aside from DRIP/BUSD. AFD (DOGS) benefits from an innovative vesting system that does not lock tokens, but reduces the variable sales tax based on the user's loyalty score.
